{{City-stub}}

==Behind the scenes==
Gesco City was first mentioned in the [[1996]] ''[[The Truce at Bakura Sourcebook]]'', which was authored by [[Kathy Tyers]] and [[Eric S. Trautmann]] for use with [[West End Games]]' ''[[Star Wars: The Roleplaying Game]]''.<ref name="Truce" />

